      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 59,
      "message": "sorry I overlooked this change in proposal, but if we do this then the path rendered would be \nGET /v2/dataspaces/my-dataspace/anchors/source-anchor/delta/target-anchor and\nPOST /v2/dataspaces/my-dataspace/anchors/source-anchor/delta\nwhich is similar to our current problem, and our objective is to have a consistent endpoint like this:\nGET /v2/dataspaces/my-dataspace/anchors/source-anchor/delta\nPOST /v2/dataspaces/my-dataspace/anchors/source-anchor/delta\nso the target anchor name should be query parameter instead of path parameter",
      "author": {
